snippet.title: L. Amber O'Hearn
snippet.description:
Videos and playlists on nutrition, especially carnivorous and ketogenic.
May contain other uploads based on my personal interests.

Please note: harassment in comments will be flagged and removed.  I may give a pointer to resources if someone asks respectfully, but I am not here to explain in depth why vegan "science" is flawed (unless that is the exact topic of a piece), or to respond to interrogation.
